{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"ida9e67801-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2861"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2861"},"text":"§ 2861.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Military construction projects in connection with industrial facility investment program","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"ida9e67802-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2861/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Authority","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary of Defense may carry out a military construction project, not previously authorized, for the purpose of carrying out activities under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s2474/a/2"},"text":"section 2474(a)(2) of this title","children":[],"tail":", using funds appropriated or otherwise made available for that purpose in military construction accounts."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"ida9e67803-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2861/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Crediting of Funds to Capital Budget","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"Funds appropriated or otherwise made available in a fiscal year for the purpose of carrying out a military construction project with respect to a covered depot (as defined in subsection (f) of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s2476"},"text":"section 2476 of this title","children":[],"tail":") may be credited to the amount required by subsection (a)(1) of such section to be invested in the capital budgets of the covered depots in that fiscal year."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"ida9e67804-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s2861/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Notice and Wait Requirement","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"When a decision is made to carry out a project under subsection (a), the Secretary of Defense shall notify the appropriate committees of Congress of that decision and the savings estimated to be realized from the project. The project may then be carried out only after the end of the 14-day period beginning on the date the notification is received by such committees in an electronic medium pursuant to ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s480"},"text":"section 480 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"ida9e67805-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"(Added ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/109/364/dB/tXXVIII/s2809/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 109–364, div. B, title XXVIII, § 2809(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2006-10-17"},"text":"Oct. 17, 2006","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/120/2470"},"text":"120 Stat. 2470","children":[],"tail":"; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/91/dA/tX/s1051/a/23"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–91, div. A, title X, § 1051(a)(23)","children":[],"tail":", div. B, title XXVIII, § 2801(c)(4), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2017-12-12"},"text":"Dec. 12, 2017","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/131/1562"},"text":"131 Stat. 1562","children":[],"tail":", 1844; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/263/dA/tIII/s374/b/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 117–263, div. A, title III, § 374(b)(2)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2022-12-23"},"text":"Dec. 23, 2022","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/136/2542"},"text":"136 Stat. 2542","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"ida9e67806-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"ida9e67807-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"priorProvisions","id":"ida9e67808-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Prior Provisions","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"A prior section 2861, added ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/214/s2/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–214, § 2(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1982-07-12"},"text":"July 12, 1982","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/96/167"},"text":"96 Stat. 167","children":[],"tail":"; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/26/s7/f/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–26, § 7(f)(1)","children":[],"tail":", (j)(9), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1987-04-21"},"text":"Apr. 21, 1987","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/101/281"},"text":"101 Stat. 281","children":[],"tail":", 283; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/106/dB/tXXVIII/s2811/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–106, div. B, title XXVIII, § 2811(b)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1996-02-10"},"text":"Feb. 10, 1996","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/110/552"},"text":"110 Stat. 552","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/201/dB/tXXVIII/s2802/d/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–201, div. B, title XXVIII, § 2802(d)(1)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1996-09-23"},"text":"Sept. 23, 1996","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/110/2787"},"text":"110 Stat. 2787","children":[],"tail":", required the Secretary of Defense to submit an annual report to the appropriate committees of Congress with respect to military construction activities and military family housing activities, prior to repeal by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/107/107/dB/tXXVIII/s2803/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 107–107, div. B, title XXVIII, § 2803(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2001-12-28"},"text":"Dec. 28, 2001","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/115/1305"},"text":"115 Stat. 1305","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"ida9e67809-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2022—Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/263"},"text":"Pub. L. 117–263","children":[],"tail":" substituted “subsection (f) of section 2476” for “subsection (e) of section 2476” and “subsection (a)(1) of such section” for “subsection (a) of such section”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2017—Subsec. (c). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/91/s2801/c/4"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–91, § 2801(c)(4)","children":[],"tail":", struck out “in writing” after “shall notify” and “or, if earlier, the end of the 14-day period beginning on the date on which a copy of the notification is provided” after “received by such committees” and substituted “14-day period” for “21-day period”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (d). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/115/91/s1051/a/23"},"text":"Pub. L. 115–91, § 1051(a)(23)","children":[],"tail":", struck out subsec. (d). Text read as follows: “Not later than December 31 of each year, the Secretary shall submit to Congress a report describing actions taken under this section and the savings realized from such actions during the fiscal year ending in the year in which the report is submitted.”"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"ida9e6780a-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"ida9e6780b-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 2022 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Amendment by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/263"},"text":"Pub. L. 117–263","children":[],"tail":" applicable with respect to fiscal years beginning on or after "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2023-10-01"},"text":"Oct. 1, 2023","children":[],"tail":", see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/263/s374/c"},"text":"section 374(c) of Pub. L. 117–263","children":[],"tail":", set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s2476"},"text":"section 2476 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
